{% block main %}
  <h1>Welcome to Montreal!</h1>

  <p class="lead">
    PGConf.dev 2025 will be held at Plaza Centre-Ville, inside the “EVO”
    building at 777 Robert-Bourassa Blvd, Montréal, QC, H3A 0B1.

